Buffett Says His `Trigger Finger Itchy' to Buy, With $38 Billion in Wallet

-- B y   R i c k   L e v i n s o n
-- 
2011-02-26T13:39:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-26/buffett-says-trigger-finger-itchy-for-takeovers-in-annual-letter.html
  Warren Buffett  said his “trigger
finger is itchy” for major aquisitions after his cash hoard at  Berkshire Hathaway Inc . climbed to $38.2 billion as of Dec. 31.  “Our elephant gun has been reloaded,” Buffett said today
in his annual letter to shareholders.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
